DAX Measures — Credit Risk Dashboard

This file documents all the key DAX measures used in my Power BI dashboard.

The goal of these measures is simple:
- Understand how the loan portfolio is performing
- Identify where risk is coming from
- Figure out which segments are actually profitable

Total Applications
Total Applications = COUNTROWS(Bank_Loan_DATA)

Total Funded
Total Funded = SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_amount])

Total Received
Total Received = SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[total_payment])

Net Return ($)
Net Return = [Total Received] - [Total Funded]

Net Return (%)
Net Return % = DIVIDE([Net Return], [Total Funded], 0)

Bad Loan Rate (%)
Bad Loan Rate % =
DIVIDE(
    CALCULATE(
        COUNTROWS(Bank_Loan_DATA),
        Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_status] = "Charged Off"
    ),
    [Total Applications],
    0
)

Recovery Rate (%)
Recovery Rate % =
DIVIDE(
    CALCULATE(
        SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[total_payment]),
        Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_status] = "Charged Off"
    ),
    CALCULATE(
        SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_amount]),
        Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_status] = "Charged Off"
    ),
    0
)

True Economic Return (%)
True Economic Return % =
DIVIDE(
    [Net Return] -
    CALCULATE(
        SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_amount] - Bank_Loan_DATA[total_payment]),
        Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_status] = "Charged Off"
    ),
    [Total Funded],
    0
)

Default Rate (%)
Default Rate % =
DIVIDE(
    CALCULATE(
        COUNTROWS(Bank_Loan_DATA),
        Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_status] = "Charged Off"
    ),
    COUNTROWS(Bank_Loan_DATA),
    0
)

LTI (Loan-to-Income Ratio)
LTI =
DIVIDE(
    Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_amount],
    Bank_Loan_DATA[annual_income],
    0
)

LTI Band
LTI Band =
SWITCH(
    TRUE(),
    [LTI] < 0.2, "Low LTI",
    [LTI] <= 0.4, "Medium LTI",
    "High LTI"
)

Net Return by Segment
Net Return Segment =
SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[total_payment]) - SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_amount])

Interest Income
Interest Income =
SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[total_payment] - Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_amount])

Charge-Off Loss
Charge-Off Loss =
CALCULATE(
    SUM(Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_amount] - Bank_Loan_DATA[total_payment]),
    Bank_Loan_DATA[loan_status] = "Charged Off"
)

